	Lefff 3.0b installation

What you need
=============

   - alexina-tools 1.2 : https://gforge.inria.fr/frs/?group_id=482
   - recode            : for the lexicon compilation


How to compile and install
==========================

   - ./configure
   - make 
   - make install (as root)


configure options
=================

--with-alexinatoolsdir=DIR	path where alexina-tools directory is installed
